<item>
            <title>[LU-7840] build of lustre 2.7 client with mellanox Ofed3.2 fails</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7840</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;trying to build Lustre 2.7 client with Mellanox OFED3.2&lt;br/&gt;
when I compile with the standard way,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;./configure --disable-server --with-o2ib=/usr/src/ofa-kernel-3.2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the configure run fails at the stage of o2ib&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&quot;can&apos;t compile with OpenIB gen2 headers under /usr/src/ofa-kernel-3.2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;when not specifying o2ib, the compilation process completes.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <environment>centos 7.1, x86_64, MLNX OFED 3.2</environment>
